source_string: Your friends and their friends can see if you're online. your game clips, and your recent apps and games. You can change these on Xbox.com.
translation: Dine venner og deres venner kan se, om du er online. De kan også se dine spilklip og dine seneste apps og spil. Dem kan du ændre på Xbox.com.

source_string: Signing in with your Microsoft account...
We could not sign you into your Microsoft account. Access to Realms, Profiles, and your Marketplace items will be limited. Please try again later.
translation: Vi kunne ikke logge dig på din Microsoft-konto. Adgangen til Realms, profiler og varer fra markedspladsen vil være begrænset. Prøv igen senere.

source_string: Failed to sign in to %s sandbox. Please change sandboxes and restart Minecraft or sign in with a different account. Sandbox will be %s on restart.
translation: Det var ikke muligt at logge på sandkassen %s. Skift sandkasse, og genstart Minecraft, eller log på med en ny konto. Sandkassen vil være %s ved genstart.

source_string: Awesome mini-games and new players are waiting for you! But first, '%s' would like to know who you are.
translation: Du kan glæde dig til fantastiske minispil og nye spillere, men i første omgang vil '%s' gerne vide, hvem du er.

source_string: You need to sign in with a Microsoft account to connect!
translation: Du skal logge på med en Microsoft-konto, inden du kan oprette forbindelse!

source_string: Sign out of your Microsoft account
Your Minecraft account lets you play online multiplayer with friends on PCs and mobile devices. And the best part?
translation: Med din Minecraft-konto kan du spille online multiplayer med dine venner på pc og mobilenheder. Og det bedste af det hele?

source_string: You can use it anywhere you play Minecraft.
translation: Du kan bruge det, alle steder du spiller Minecraft.

source_string: Sign in with your Microsoft account to play with friends.
translation: Log på med din Microsoft-konto for at spille med dine venner.

source_string: This Microsoft account does not have permission to join multiplayer games.
translation: Microsoft-kontoen har ikke tilladelse til at deltage i multiplayerspil.

source_string: You must be friends with someone in this game in order to join.
translation: Du skal være venner med nogen i spillet for at kunne deltage.

source_string: Success! %s was added to your friend list.
Favorite friends go first on your friends list. You'll see when they go online or start broadcasting.
translation: Dine bedste venner vises først på din venneliste. Du kan se, når de går online eller starter en udsendelse.

source_string: Follow %s. After you both are friends, you can invite them to your game.
translation: Følg %s. Når I er venner med hinanden, kan du invitere vedkommende til dit spil.

source_string: Manage your privacy settings for sharing your real name in the Xbox app.
translation: Administrer indstillingerne for deling af dit rigtige navn i Xbox-appen.

source_string: An issue occurred while attempting to open the Player profile. Error Code: %d
translation: Der opstod et problem under forsøget på at åbne spillerprofilen. Fejlkode: %d

source_string: We were unable to send your report. Try again soon.
translation: Vi kunne ikke sende din indberetning. Prøv igen senere.

source_string: Where did you observe the bad behavior?
translation: Hvor så du den dårlige opførsel?

source_string: Please let us know where the incident took place. This will help us in researching your case.
translation: Fortæl os, hvor hændelsen fandt sted. Det hjælper os med at undersøge din sag.

source_string: Impersonating staff, Player Support, or Community representatives
translation: Udgiver sig for at være ansat, spillersupport eller repræsentant for community

source_string: Posting links to inappropriate content or malicious software
translation: Angiver links til upassende indhold eller skadelig software
Oplysninger fra det virkelige liv eller trusler
Henvisninger til seksuelt indhold eller vold
Seksuel udnyttelse eller misbrug af børn

source_string: You've been temporarily muted in chat.
translation: Du er blevet midlertidigt slået fra i chatten.

source_string: Remember to follow the Minecraft Community Standards.

Your current skin violates our Community Standards. Please select a different skin to join a multiplayer game. Click "%s" to view our Community Standards or submit a case review for your current skin.
translation: Dit nuværende skin overtræder vores fællesskabsregler. Vælg et andet skin for at deltage i et multiplayerspil. Klik "%s" for at se vores fællesskabsregler eller indsende en sagsanmeldelse for dit nuværende skin.

source_string: §eChat and other user generated text is not available on this realm right now. Please try again later.§f
translation: §eChat og anden brugergenereret tekst er ikke tilgængelig på dette realm lige nu. Prøv igen senere.§f

source_string: Something went wrong. We can't verify that the server you are trying to connect to is one that we trust. We recommend that you try again later.
translation: Vi kan ikke verificere pålideligheden af den server, du forsøger at oprette forbindelse til. Vi anbefaler, at du prøver igen senere.

source_string: This is bad. This server failed our verification test. Someone we don't trust might be pretending to be a trusted server.
translation: Det var ikke så godt. Serveren bestod ikke vores verificeringstest. Nogen udgiver sig muligvis for at være en pålidelig server uden at være det.

source_string: You've been playing for greater than 24 hours
translation: Du har spillet i mere end 24 timer

source_string: Excessive gaming may interfere with normal daily life
translation: Overdrevet spil kan forstyrre en normal hverdag

source_string: The property '%s' is not used for this type of content. The field will be ignored.

translation: Egenskaben '%s' har en version af '%s', der er for høj. Den højeste accepterede værdi er '%s'.

translation: Egenskaben '%s' skal have en værdi under '%s'. Hvis du vil bruge en højere version, skal du anvende formatversion 2.

source_string: Folder structure in pack is too deep.

translation: Elementet '%s' mangler i pakkemanifestet; '%s' anvendes i stedet.

translation: Du er ved at slette denne ressource-/adfærdspakke for evigt. Er du sikker?

source_string: Editor extension packs can only be used on Editor projects. Your world will still load, however we recommend deactivating or deleting the extension packs.
translation: Editor-udvidelsespakker kan kun bruges på Editor-projekter. Din verden vil stadig blive indlæst, men vi anbefaler, at du deaktiverer eller sletter udvidelsespakkerne.

source_string: %s: Child controls must have unique names: %sIn the future this will be an error and this file won't load.
translation: %s: Underordnede objekter skal have unikke navne: %sFremover antages dette som en fejl, så filen ikke kan indlæses.

translation: Indholdet i denne verden understøttes ikke af Minecraft Education.

source_string: Would you like to play your world now?
translation: Vil du spille i din egen verden nu?

source_string: Adding an external server requires knowing the server name and server IP address. Once added, the server can be found in the server list for play.
translation: Hvis du vil tilføje en ekstern server, skal du kende serverens navn og IP-adresse. Når serveren er tilføjet, vises den på serverlisten til spil.

source_string: This server has already been added

translation: Det tog for lang tid at indlæse

source_string: Got stuck on an error message
translation: Kunne ikke fortsætte pga. en fejlmeddelelse
Der blev stillet for mange spørgsmål

source_string: I didn't know it was free
translation: Jeg vidste ikke, det var gratis

source_string: I thought I needed a Xbox console
translation: Jeg troede, jeg skulle bruge en Xbox-konsol
context: disable_3rd_party_console_resource_pack_check

source_string: Feedback: Why didn't you sign in?
translation: Feedback: Hvorfor loggede du ikke på?

source_string: You can hold down Shift to take a close up picture using the Camera.
translation: Du kan tage et nærbillede med kameraet ved at holde Shift nede.

source_string: Unlike Signs, you can edit Slates, Posters, and Boards over and over again.
translation: I modsætning til skilte kan du redigere tavler, plakater og kridttavler om og om igen.

source_string: Use Ctrl+B to turn on text-to-speech capabilities for in-game chat.
translation: Tryk på Ctrl+B for at aktivere tekst til tale-funktioner i spillets chat.

source_string: You can export your Minecraft world to share it with others.
translation: Du kan eksportere din Minecraft-verden, hvis du vil dele den med andre.

source_string: To have your peers connect to your world, pause your game and share your join code.
translation: Når du vil have andre til at oprette forbindelse til din verden, skal du sætte spillet på pause og dele din deltagerkode.

source_string: Remember that to use slash commands, you need to enable cheats in your world.
translation: Husk, at du kun kan bruge skråstregskommandoer, når du har aktiveret snydekoder i din verden.

source_string: Done with your creation? Have others tour your world as visitors to protect your work.
translation: Er du færdig med at oprette? Få andre til at besøge din verden som gæster, så dit arbejde er beskyttet.

source_string: To code in Minecraft, press "C" on your keyboard or touch the Agent icon at the top of your screen.
translation: Du koder i Minecraft ved at trykke på "C" på dit tastatur eller trykke på Agent-ikonet øverst på din skærm.

source_string: Use the Library to find new game worlds to build in.
translation: Brug biblioteket til at finde nye spilverdener at bygge i.

source_string: Looking for a specific biome? Try the Library.
translation: Leder du efter et specifikt biom? Prøv at kigge i biblioteket.

source_string: In Survival Mode, players must find their own resources.
translation: I Overlevelse skal spillerne finde deres egne ressourcer.

source_string: In Creative Mode, players can freely choose to build from any of the blocks in Minecraft.
translation: I Kreativ kan spillere frit vælge at bygge med alle typer blokke i Minecraft.

source_string: Your code building robot helper is called the Agent.
Redstone can be used in Minecraft to create circuits and simple machines.
translation: Redstone kan bruges i Minecraft til at lave kredsløb og simple maskiner.

source_string: You can copy and paste from a text editor to a slate, poster, board, or into chat.
translation: Du kan copy-paste fra en teksteditor til chatten og til kridttavler i alle størrelser.

source_string: Show hints for commonly-used keyboard and mouse controls by pressing "H" on your keyboard.
translation: Du kan se de mest almindelige former for styring med tastatur og mus ved at trykke på "H" på tastaturet.

source_string: You can toggle Auto Jump on or off in the Settings menu under Controls.
translation: Du kan slå Automatisk hop til eller fra i menuen Indstillinger under Kontrolelementer.

source_string: While in Creative Mode, quickly press jump twice to fly.
translation: I Kreativ skal du trykke hurtigt to gange for at flyve.

source_string: Choose a Default Game Mode when creating a world to specify the type of gameplay you want.
translation: Vælg en standardspiltilstand, der passer til dit gameplay, når du opretter en verden.

source_string: Use the command "/setworldspawn" to have new players begin playing where you are standing.
translation: Brug kommandoen ''/setworldspawn'' for at få nye spillere til at spille, hvor du står.

source_string: Choose a default player permission when creating your world to specify the permissions you want your classmates to have when they join.
translation: Vælg en standardspillertilladelse, når du opretter din verden, for at angive de tilladelser, du ønsker, at klassekammeraterne skal have, når de deltager.

source_string: Press "I" on your keyboard or touch the Immersive Reader icon to read or translate in-game text.
translation: Tryk på "I" på dit tastatur eller på ikonet for Moderne læser for at læse eller oversætte tekst i spillet.

source_string: To add or change an NPC in your world, first make yourself a world builder with "/wb".
translation: Hvis du vil tilføje eller ændre en NPC i din verden, skal du først gøre dig selv til verdensbygger med "/wb".

source_string: There's a brand new build challenge every month! Find them all in the Library under Monthly Build Challenges.
translation: Der kommer en ny byggeudfordring hver eneste måned! Du finder dem i biblioteket under Månedens byggeudfordringer.

source_string: Find related lessons by clicking on tags in the Library.
translation: Find relaterede lektioner ved at klikke på tags i biblioteket.

source_string: Game moving slowly? Try turning down the render distance in Settings.
translation: Er spillet blevet langsomt? Prøv at skrue ned for synslængden i Indstillinger.

source_string: Want to use Code Builder? Make sure cheats are toggled on.
translation: Vil du bruge Code Builder? Sørg for at aktivere snydekoder.

source_string: Press F5 to change player perspective.
translation: Tryk på F5 for at ændre spillerperspektivet.

source_string: Use "/spawnpoint" to change your spawn point. It's just like you slept in a bed!
translation: Brug "/spawnpoint" til at ændre dit spawningspunkt. Det er, lige som hvis du sov i en seng!

source_string: Most monsters only come out at night. During the day you're safe... probably.
translation: De fleste monstre kommer kun frem om natten. I løbet af dagen er du sikker ... vistnok.

source_string: Break blocks, pick up resources. Use the crafting grid to make helpful items. Now you're crafting!
translation: Bryd blokke, saml ressourcer. Brug fremstillingsgitteret til at lave nyttige genstande. Sådan fremstiller du!

source_string: You have endless lives, but your items drop to the ground when you die. Hurry back to pick them up!
translation: Du har endeløse liv, men dine genstande dropper til jorden, når du dør. Skynd dig tilbage for at samle dem op!

source_string: It's a good idea to build a place where you can safely spend the night.
translation: Det er en god idé at bygge et sted, hvor du kan tilbringe natten i sikkerhed.

source_string: Use the right tool for the job! Chopping wood with an axe is much faster than using your hands.
translation: Brug det rigtige værktøj til opgaven! Det er meget hurtigere at hugge brænde med en økse end med dine bare hænder.

source_string: Even in Minecraft you'll get hungry, so try to find something to eat before that happens.
translation: Selv i Minecraft bliver du sulten, så prøv at finde noget at spise, før det sker.

source_string: Digging straight down or straight up might not be a great idea.
translation: Det er måske ikke en særlig god idé at grave direkte ned eller direkte op.

source_string: Monsters spawn in the dark. Craft a torch to brighten up any space.
translation: Monstre spawner i mørket. Fremstil en fakkel, så du kan lyse alle rum op.

source_string: Beds are great! Craft one to quickly pass the night and set your respawn point.
translation: Senge er fantastiske! Fremstil en for hurtigt at komme igennem natten til og fastsætte dit respawnpunkt.

source_string: Be careful when you swim. Stay under water for too long and you'll run out of air.
translation: Vær forsigtig, når du svømmer. Hvid du bliver for længe under vandet, løber du tør for luft.

source_string: Survival mode has 4 different difficulty levels - Peaceful, Easy, Normal, and Hard. Or play Creative mode and get endless resources!
translation: Overlevelsestilstand har 4 forskellige sværhedsgrader: fredfyldt, let, normal og svær. Eller spil i kreativ tilstand, og få endeløse ressourcer!

source_string: The world of Minecraft is endlessly surprising. You'll find lots of different animals, plants, and even §f§k§a§b§r §f§k§a§b§r
translation: Minecrafts verden er uendeligt overraskende. Du finder masser af forskellige dyr, planter og endda §f§k§a§b§r §f§k§a§b§r
context: please leave "§f§k§a§b§r" unchanged

source_string: Iron golems will fight for you!
Feed a bone to a wolf to tame it. You can then make it sit or follow you.
translation: Giv en knogle til en ulv for at tæmme den. Du kan derefter få den til at sitte eller følge dig.

source_string: Wearing a pumpkin on your head will keep Endermen from attacking you.
translation: Hvis du tager et græskar på hovedet, vil du afholde endermen fra at angribe dig.

source_string: Harvest leather from cows, and use it to make armor and books.
translation: Høst læder fra køer, og brug det til at fremstille rustning og bøger.

source_string: You can fill an empty bucket with water, lava, milk, powdered snow... and even some mobs.
translation: Du kan fylde en tom spand med vand, lava, mælk, pulversne ... og endda visse mobs.

source_string: Feeding an animal will keep it from despawning. Build a pen to keep your animals safe.
translation: Hvis du fodrer et dyr, afholder du det fra at despawne. Byg en indhegning for at holde dine dyr i sikkerhed.

source_string: Get to your destination faster with a minecart and some rails!
translation: Nå hurtigere frem til din destination med en minevogn og nogle skinner!

source_string: Building a portal will allow you to travel to another dimension called the Nether.
translation: Når du bygger en portal, kan du rejse til en anden dimension, der kaldes Nether.

source_string: Bonemeal (crafted from a skeleton bone) can be used as a fertilizer and can make things grow instantly!
translation: Benmel (fremstillet af en skeletknogle) kan bruges som gødning og få tingene til at vokse med det samme!

source_string: Obsidian is created when water hits a lava source block.
translation: Obsidian skabes, når vand rammer en lava-kildeblok.

source_string: If the source block for water or lava is removed, it will stop the flow completely.
translation: Hvis kildeblokken for vand eller lava fjernes, stopper den strømmen helt.

source_string: Blocks that can be used as a light source will melt snow and ice.
translation: Blokke, der kan bruges som en lyskilde, smelter sne og is.

source_string: Take caution when building structures made of wool out in the open, as lightning from thunderstorms can set wool on fire.
translation: Vær forsigtig, når du bygger strukturer, der er fremstillet af uld, ude i det åbne, for lyn fra tordenvejr kan sætte ild til uld.

source_string: A single bucket of lava can be used in a furnace to smelt 100 blocks.
translation: En enkelt spand lava kan bruges i en ovn til at smelte 100 blokke.

source_string: The instrument played by a note block depends on the material beneath it.
translation: Instrumentet, der afspilles af en nodeblok, afhænger af materialet under den.

source_string: Attacking a wolf will cause any wolves nearby to turn hostile and attack you.
translation: Angriber du en ulv, vil det gøre ulve i nærheden fjendtlige, så de angriber dig.

source_string: Wolves and iron golems won't attack creepers.
translation: Ulve og jerngolemmer angriber ikke creepere.

source_string: Chickens lay an egg every 5 to 10 minutes.
translation: Kyllinger lægger et æg hvert 5. til 10. minut.

source_string: Obsidian can be mined with a diamond pickaxe.
translation: Obsidian kan udvindes med en diamanthakke.

source_string: Creepers are the easiest obtainable source of gunpowder.
translation: Creepere er den kilde til krudt, der er nemmest at få fat på.

source_string: Tame wolves show their health with the position of their tail. Feed them meat to heal them.
translation: Tamme ulve viser deres helbred med positionen på deres hale. Giv dem kød for at helbrede dem.

source_string: Different colored dyes can be made from a variety of materials, cook cactus in a furnace to get green dye!
translation: Forskellige farver kan fremstilles af en række materialer, kog kaktusser i en ovn for at få grøn farve!

source_string: Pigs that are struck by lightning become zombified piglins.
translation: Grise, der rammes af lynet, bliver zombificerede pigliner.
Endermen hader at gå i bad!

source_string: Sometimes iron golems give flowers to the villager children!
translation: Jerngolemmer kan finde på at give blomster til børn i landsbyer!
Ozelotter viser creepere, hvem der bestemmer!

source_string: Use seagrass to attract and breed sea turtles.
translation: Brug havgræs til at tiltrække og avle på havskildpadder.

source_string: Protect baby turtles from hostile mobs!
Baby turtles will drop scutes when they grow - these can be crafted into turtle shells.
translation: Babyskildpadder dropper skæl, når de vokser – skæl kan bruges til at fremstille skildpaddeskjold.

source_string: Brew some water breathing potions for underwater exploration!
translation: Bryg gælleeliksirer, så du kan gå på opdagelse under vandet!

source_string: Dolphins can lead you to shipwrecks and underwater ruins, feed them cod and follow their trail!
translation: Delfiner kan føre dig til skibsvrag og ruiner under vandet – forkæl dem med lidt torsk, og følg deres spor!

source_string: Use shears to carve a pumpkin.
translation: Brug en saks til at skære græskar ud.

source_string: There are 3587 types of tropical fish!
Sea pickles can be smelted into lime green dye.
translation: Søpølser kan smeltes til limegrøn farve.

source_string: Use hay bales to breed Llamas!
translation: Brug høballer til at avle på lamaer!

source_string: Compasses always point to the world spawn - craft one to find your way!
translation: Et kompas peger altid mod verdens spawnpunkt – fremstil et, så du kan finde vej!

source_string: Trade with villagers to obtain food, tools, and even explorer maps!
translation: Få fingrene i mad, værktøj og måske endda udforskerkort ved at handle med landsbyboere.

source_string: Did you know you can hold a map in your off-hand?
translation: Du kan holde et kort i din ikkeforetrukne hånd.

source_string: Leads can be used on boats.
Sneak to walk safely on magma blocks.
translation: Du kan gå hen over magmablokke uden at brænde dig, hvis du sniger.

source_string: You can gather cobwebs using shears.
translation: Du kan indsamle spindelvæv med en saks.

source_string: Tridents are dropped by the Drowned, and can be held or thrown.
translation: Drauger dropper treforker. De kan både kastes og bruges til nærkamp.

source_string: You can smelt 20 items in a furnace by using a block of dried kelp as fuel.
translation: Du kan smelte op til 20 genstande i en ovn ved at bruge en blok tørret tang som brændsel.

source_string: Taming a skeleton horse doesn't require a saddle.
translation: Du har ikke brug for en sadel for at tæmme en skelethest.

source_string: Phantoms are dangerous mobs that appear during the night. Make sure to sleep regularly!
translation: Fantomer er farlige væsner, der kun viser sig om natten. Husk at få din nattesøvn!

source_string: Zombies turn into drowned if they sink underwater.
translation: Zombier bliver til drauger, hvis de synker ned under vandet.
Du svømmer ved at spurte i vandet!
Lad være med at dræbe delfiner, dit monster!

source_string: When digging straight up, place a torch at your feet to break any sand or gravel that could potentially fall down on you.
translation: Placer en fakkel ved dine fødder, når du graver direkte opad, så du ødelægger sand og grus, der falder ned på dig.

source_string: Shear a Beehive or nest to get Honeycomb, use a Bottle to get honey.
translation: Du kan klippe bikager ud af bistader og bikuber eller hælde honningen på flasker.

source_string: Place a campfire under a beehive or nest to harvest honey.
translation: Placér et lejrbål under en bistade eller rede for at høste honning.

source_string: Emerald ores are the rarest ores in Minecraft! They can only be found in mountains and meadows.
translation: Smaragdmalm er den sjældneste malm i Minecraft! Den findes udelukkende i bjerge og enge.

source_string: Need diamonds? They get more common as you go deeper.
translation: Mængden af diamanter stiger, jo længere ned du kommer.

source_string: Frogs eat small and blocky mobs.
translation: Frøer spiser små og blokkede mobs.

source_string: The Allay loves to collect items! If you give it a certain item it will try to collect more of it.
translation: Allayen er en samler! Hvis du giver den en ting, forsøger den at samle flere af samme slags.

source_string: Frogs pick a variant based on the temperature of the biome the tadpole grow up in.
translation: Frøer varierer efter temperaturen i det biom, haletudsen et vokset op i.

source_string: You can collect tadpoles in buckets.
translation: Du kan samle haletudser i spande.

source_string: Ancient cities can be found under mountain ranges.
Allays love music and therefore interact with noteblocks!
translation: Allayer elsker musik og interagerer derfor med nodeblokke!

source_string: Use a water bottle on a dirt block to get mud!
translation: Brug en vandflaske på en jordblok for at få mudder!

source_string: When wandering in the deep dark, silence is key.
translation: Stilhed er nøglen, når du vandrer omkring i det dybe mørke.

source_string: Some animals will follow you if you have wheat in your hand.
translation: Nogle dyr følger dig, hvis du har hvede i hånden.

source_string: Before you mine diamonds, redstone, or gold, make sure you're using an iron or diamond pickaxe or it won't work.
translation: Hvis du vil udvinde diamanter, rødsten eller guld, skal du bruge en hakke af jern eller diamant, ellers virker det ikke.

source_string: Placing two chests side by side will make one large chest.
translation: Placerer du to kister ved siden af hinanden, får du én stor kiste.

source_string: Can't find any coal for your torches? Try putting some logs in a furnace.
translation: Kan du ikke finde kul til dine fakler? Prøv at lægge nogle kævler i en ovn.

source_string: Plant some saplings and they'll grow into trees.
translation: Hvis du planter nogle stiklinger, vokser de op og bliver til træer.

source_string: Use a hoe to prepare areas of ground for planting.
translation: Brug et lugejern til at forberede jordområder til plantning.

source_string: Zombified piglins won't attack you - unless you make them angry.
translation: Zombificerede pigliner angriber dig ikke – medmindre du gør dem vrede.

source_string: Hit those fireballs back at the Ghast!
Cobblestone is resistant to Ghast fireballs, making it useful for guarding portals.
translation: Brosten er modstandsdygtigt over for Ghast-ildkugler, hvilket gør dem nyttige til at vogte portaler.

source_string: Our music is by C418, Lena Raine, Aaron Cherof, and Kumi Tanioka.
translation: Vores musik er af C418, Lena Raine, Aaron Cherof og Kumi Tanioka.

source_string: There will be an update to this game eventually!
translation: På et tidspunkt kommer der en opdatering til spillet!

source_string: Creepers were born from a coding bug.
translation: Creepere opstod på grund af kodefejl.

source_string: The first version of Minecraft was created in just 6 days!
translation: Den første version af Minecraft blev skabt på bare seks dage!

source_string: The Enderman language is actually English in reverse.
The original name for Minecraft was Cave Game.
translation: Minecrafts originale navn var Cave Game.

source_string: A Spider Jockey is the rare appearance of a spider being ridden by a skeleton!
translation: En edderkopjockey er det sjældne tilfælde, hvor et skelet rider på en edderkop!

source_string: Traveling one block in the Nether is equal to traveling eight blocks in the Overworld.
translation: En afstand på én blok i Nether svarer til otte blokke i oververdenen.

source_string: Use phantom membranes to repair your elytra.
translation: Brug membraner fra fantomer til at reparere din elytra.

source_string: Elytra can be used to glide, find them in End city ships!
translation: Elytra kan bruges til at svæve. Find dem i skibe fra End-byer!

source_string: Test out some new features by turning on Experimental Gameplay in the settings menu!
translation: Test nogle nye funktioner ved at aktivere eksperimentelt gameplay i indstillingsmenuen!

source_string: Monsters that are killed by skeletons arrows have a chance of dropping music discs.
translation: Monstre, der dræbes af pile fra skeletter, dropper af og til musikplader.

source_string: Texture packs change the way that blocks, items, and even the menus look in game. Try them out!
translation: Teksturpakker ændrer udseendet af blokke, genstande og endda menuer i spillet. Giv dem et skud!

source_string: Using firework rockets boosts elytra speed in mid air. Just... make sure they don't explode, otherwise it'll hurt BADLY!
translation: Brug fyrværkeriraketter til at sætte farten op på din elytra, mens du er i luften ... bare pas på, det hele ikke eksploderer – det gør ONDT!
Er der egentlig nogen, der læser det her?

source_string: Riptide enchantment will propel you through the air in the rain.
translation: Hvis du bruger fortryllelsen Understrøm, når det regner, bliver du selv kastet fremad.

source_string: The Beacon is a powerful item that can only be crafted with a Nether star from the Wither!
translation: Fyret er en kraftfuld genstand, der kun kan fremstilles med en Nether-stjerne fra Wither!

source_string: Nether stars can't be destroyed by explosions.
translation: Nether-stjerner kan ikke ødelægges af eksplosioner.

source_string: Respawning in the Nether requires a charged respawn anchor.
translation: Respawning i Nether kræver et opladet respawn-anker.

source_string: You can charge a respawn anchor with glowstone.
translation: Du kan oplade et respawn-anker med glødesten.

source_string: You can breed hoglins with crimson fungus, but be careful.
translation: Du kan avle hoglins med blodrøde svampe, men vær forsigtig!

source_string: Gold is most common in the Nether and in the badlands biome.
translation: Guld er mest almindeligt i Nether og i badlandsbiomet.

source_string: Diorite, you either love it or hate it.
translation: Diorit – du enten elsker eller hader det.

source_string: Take a screenshot using the Game menu.
translation: Tag et skærmbillede ved hjælp af spilmenuen.

source_string: A Realm is always online, so you and your friends can play here whenever you want.
translation: Et realm er altid online, så du og dine venner kan spille her, når som helst I vil.

source_string: Keep up to date with what's going on in your Realm by checking the Story Feed in Realms Stories.
translation: Hold dig opdateret med det, der foregår i dit realm ved at tjekke fortællingsfeedet i Realms Stories.

source_string: Share your great moments with the other players on this Realm by adding a story to the Story Feed.
translation: Del dine store øjeblikke med de andre spillere i dette realm ved at tilføje en historie til fortællingsfeed.

source_string: Check the Timeline in Realms Stories to find out when others are playing.
translation: Tjek tidslinjen i Realms Stories for at finde ud af, hvornår andre spiller.

source_string: Access Realms Stories from the game menu while playing on the Realm.
translation: Få adgang til Realms Stories fra spilmenuen, mens du spiller på realmet.

source_string: Get to know your Realm's community on the Members tab in Realms Stories.
translation: Lær dit Realms-fællesskab at kende på fanen Medlemmer i Realms Stories.

source_string: Use Realms Stories to get social, keep up with your friends' progress, and organize playtime.
translation: Brug Realms Stories til at være social, holde trit med dine venners fremskridt og planlægge spilletid.

source_string: Bored of gravity? Jump twice to fly!
translation: Træt af tyngdekraften? Hop to gange for at flyve!
context: A fun way to tell players that they can fly if they press the jump button twice.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Summon mobs in an instant with spawn eggs.
translation: Tilkald mobs på et øjeblik med spawnæg.
context: Players can use an item called Sawn Egg to summon animals and monsters.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Collect goat horns and fill the world with music.
translation: Saml gedehorn, og fyld verden med musik.
context: Goat horn is an object players can use to play loud sounds.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Combine flint and steel with a TNT block for explosive results.
translation: Kombinér flint og stål med en TNT-blok, og få eksplosive resultater.
context: Flint and steel is a tool used to create fire or to ignite certain blocks, structures and mobs. TNT will explode when you light it.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Try blinking around the map with an ender pearl. Don't get dizzy!
translation: Prøv at blinke rundt på kortet med en enderperle. Bliv ikke svimmel!
context: An ender pearl is an item that can be thrown and teleports the thrower to where it lands.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Use rails and a minecart to build the perfect transport system. Or rollercoaster!
translation: Brug skinner og en minevogn til at bygge det perfekte transportsystem. Eller rutsjebane!
context: To  encourage players to build railroads{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Seeking a little more danger? Survival mode has plenty.
translation: Leder du efter lidt mere fare? Overlevelsestilstand har masser.
context: In the Game mode Survival mode you can die. In Creative you can’t.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Crossbows need ammo. Add some arrows to your inventory before going hunting.
translation: Armbrøster har brug for ammunition. Tilføj nogle pile til dit lager, før du går på jagt.
context: Crossbows need ammo. Add some arrows to your inventory before going hunting.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: You can't die, but villagers can. Use that information... wisely.
translation: Du kan ikke dø, men det kan landsbyboere kan. Brug disse oplysninger ... klogt.
context: This means you can do things that will get villagers killed. Like attracting monsters to the village.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Villagers are great at building villages. Think you can do better?
translation: Landsbyboere er gode til at bygge landsbyer. Tror du, at du kan gøre det bedre?
context: This is a prompt to encourage players to build things.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Wolves will attack skeletons to chew on their tasty bones.
translation: Ulve angriber skeletter for at tygge på deres lækre knogler.
context: Wolves will attack skeletons. It’s also a discrete hint that you should feel wolves with bones to tame them.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Tame wild horses by sitting on them until they're calm, then saddle up and ride off. (Note: Horses do not work like that outside of Minecraft.)
translation: Tæm vilde heste ved at sidde på dem, indtil de er rolige, og sadl derefter op, og rid afsted. (Bemærk: Sådan fungerer heste ikke sådan uden for Minecraft.)
context: It’s a bit unintuitive how you tame horses. Most other animals are tamed by feeding them. Not Horses. {MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Eat as much as you want, you'll never get full! And you'll never starve.
translation: Spis så meget, du vil, du bliver aldrig mæt! Og du vil aldrig sulte.
context: In Creative Mode you don’t get hungry. Eating the food it just for fun.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Move through solid objects using spectator mode.
translation: Bevæg dig gennem massive genstande ved hjælp af tilskuertilstand.
context: There is a Game mode called Spectator Mode. It allows you to fly through walls and blocks and everything.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Who needs tools? Punch your way to success and remove blocks instantly in creative mode.
translation: Hvem har brug for værktøj? Slå dig vej til succes, og fjern blokke med det samme i kreativ tilstand.
context: Block breaking happens very fast when you’re in Creative Mode.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Like what you see? Use the pick block button to start building with whatever you're looking at. Yes, even mobs!
translation: Kan du lide det, du ser? Brug knappen Vælg blok til at begynde at bygge med hvad du end du måtte kigge på. Ja, selv mobs!
context: There is a feature called “Pick block” that enables players to instantly equip any block they click on. If you click on a mob(animal or monster) you will get a spawn egg that summons another monster/animal of that kind.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Get there now with the /tp command.
context: You can teleport yourself in Creative. You use the /tp command in the chat.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Mobs won't notice you in creative mode, but they'll still notice each other…
translation: Mobs vil ikke lægge mærke til dig i kreativ tilstand, men de vil stadig lægge mærke til hinanden ...
context: Mobs(animals & monsters) won’t notice you in creative mode, but they’ll still notice each other… meaning that they can still kill each other.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: A warden a day keeps the… well, everything away.
translation: En warden om dagen holder ... tja, alt væk.
context: The Warden is a scary monster that live in underground cities.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Why not build an underwater base? It's not like you can drown.
translation: Hvorfor bygger du ikke en undervandsbase? Det er ikke, fordi at du kan drukne.
context: You can’t drown in creative mode. So it’s possible to build underwater without danger.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Whatever you can dream, you can build. There's no limit to your resources (in creative mode...).
translation: Hvad du kan drømme, kan du bygge. Der er ingen grænser for dine ressourcer (i kreativ tilstand ...).
context: Players have endless resources in Creative mode. They get all the building blocks from their inventory.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Phantoms can't hurt you, but you can still shoo them off by using a bed. Just...not literally. You sleep in it.
translation: Fantomer kan ikke skade dig, men du kan stadig genne dem væk ved at bruge en seng. Bare ... ikke i bogstavelig forstand. Du sover i den.
context: Phantoms are flying mobs(monsters) that spawn when you havn't slept for a few days. They won't hurt you in Creative Mode. To get rid of them you sleep in a bed.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: Have you tried swimming in lava? It's like sinking into a warm bath. Just don't try it in survival mode...
translation: Har du prøvet at svømme i lava? Det er som at synke ned i et varmt bad. Bare lad være med at prøve det i overlevelsestilstand ...
context: Lava doesn't hurt you in creative mode.{MaxLength="200"}

source_string: A second player can't join right now.
translation: Andre spillere kan ikke være med lige nu.

source_string: You have too many controllers connected while in Local Network Mode to join this game.
translation: Du kan ikke deltage, fordi der er tilsluttet for mange controllere i det lokale netværk.

source_string: Some worlds are not available because they could not be moved. Restart Minecraft to try again.
translation: Nogle verdener kunne ikke flyttes. Genstart Minecraft for at prøve igen.

source_string: Read the FAQ for more info.
You don't have enough free space to move your files to a new location.
translation: Du har ikke plads nok til at flytte dine filer til en ny placering.

source_string: We need to move your files to a different location on your device.
translation: Vi er nødt til at flytte dine filer til en anden placering på din enhed.

source_string: We're in the middle of moving your data to a new location on your device. Please press resume to finish the move.
translation: Vi er ved at flytte dine data til en ny placering på din enhed. Tryk på Genoptag for at færdiggøre flytningen.

source_string: We're in the middle of moving your data to a new location on your device, but you don't have enough free space.
translation: Vi er ved at flytte dine data til en ny placering på din enhed, men du har ikke nok ledig plads.

source_string: Please free up at least %s to continue.
Your files have been moved successfully. Please restart Minecraft.
translation: Dine filer er blevet flyttet. Genstart Minecraft.

source_string: We couldn't move all your files. We encountered the following error: (%s).
translation: Vi kunne ikke flytte alle dine filer. Vi løb ind i følgende fejl: (%s).

source_string: Failed (file I/O error or no space left)
Select "Delete Now" to delete all previous log files.
translation: Tryk på "Slet nu" for at slette alle logfiler.

source_string: Note: The log file for your currently active session will remain.
translation: Bemærk: Logfilen for din aktuelle aktive session slettes ikke.

source_string: Based on your recent support ticket, Mojang Player Support has granted permission to upload your world. You can upload your affected world from the World Select screen or under World Settings.
translation: Baseret på din seneste supportanmodning har Mojangs spillersupport givet tilladelse til at uploade din verden. Du kan uploade din berørte verden fra skærmen Vælg verden eller under Verdensindstillinger.

source_string: Do not show this screen again

translation: Erklæring om beskyttelse af personlige oplysninger

source_string: To upload your world, accept the Microsoft Services Agreement. Uploaded worlds are subject to the Microsoft Services Agreement, which can be found under Terms of Use. You can still play with your world once uploaded.
translation: Du skal acceptere Microsoft-serviceaftalen, inden du kan uploade din verden. Uploadede verdener er underlagt Microsoft-serviceaftalen, som kan findes under Vilkår for anvendelse. Du kan stadig spille i din verden, når den er uploadet.

source_string: Uploading your world files may take a few minutes. Do not turn off the game or leave this screen during the upload process.
translation: Det kan tage et par minutter at uploade dine verdensfiler. Sluk ikke for spillet, og bliv på denne skærm under uploadprocessen.

source_string: World sizes can be large. Please connect to WiFi to avoid using mobile data.
translation: Verdener kan være store. Opret forbindelse til wi-fi, så du ikke bruger mobildata.

source_string: Your world upload has completed successfully. Thank you!
translation: Din verden er uploadet. Tak skal du have!

source_string: Your world could not be uploaded because %s
translation: Din verden kunne ikke uploades, fordi %s

source_string: Your world could not be uploaded because %s
translation: Din verden kunne ikke uploades, fordi %s

source_string: it consists of too many files. Please get in touch with LiveOps if you want to try again.
translation: den består af for mange filer. Kontakt LiveOps, hvis du vil prøve igen.

source_string: one of the files is too big. Please get in touch with LiveOps if you want to try again.
translation: en af filerne er for stor. Kontakt LiveOps, hvis du vil prøve igen.

source_string: it has already been successfully uploaded. Please get in touch with LiveOps for more information.
translation: den allerede er uploadet. Kontakt LiveOps for at få flere oplysninger.

source_string: of a network error. Please try again or get in touch with LiveOps.
translation: der opstod en netværksfejl. Prøv igen, eller kontakt LiveOps.

source_string: of an unknown error. Please try again or get in touch with LiveOps. (Error code: %s)
translation: der opstod en ukendt fejl. Prøv igen, eller kontakt LiveOps. (Fejlkode: %s)

source_string: Import a png (64x32, 64x64, or 128x128) from your device to use as your skin. This will not sync between devices or games.
translation: Importér en png (64x32, 64x64, or 128x128) fra din enhed for at bruge den som dit skin. Dette synkroniseres ikke mellem enheder eller spil.

source_string: Your device cannot select a custom skin while in a multiplayer game. Please return to the main menu to equip one.
translation: Din enhed kan ikke vælge et tilpasset skin, mens du er i et multiplayerspil. Vend tilbage til hovedmenuen for at anvende et.

source_string: Players with custom skins will not be visible to you if the “Only Allow Trusted Skins” option is enabled
translation: Hvis du aktiverer indstillingen "Tillad kun sikre skins", kan du ikke se andre spilleres brugerdefinerede skins

source_string: Please import a .png file of dimensions 64x64, 64x32, or 128x128
This skin can be used here, but may not roam.
translation: Dette skin kan bruges her, men flyttes muligvis ikke globalt.

source_string: This skin will roam wherever you've logged in.
translation: Skinnet følger med overalt, når du logger på.

source_string: *Buys %s Minecoins for %s and redeems this pack for %s Minecoins leaving %s left over.
translation: *Giver dig %s Minecoins for %s og indløser pakken for %s Minecoins, så der er %s tilbage.

source_string: Choose the correct model type for your skin
translation: Vælg den korrekte modeltype for dit skin

source_string: You must purchase the skin pack to use that skin, and we can't connect to the Marketplace.
translation: Du skal købe skinpakken, inden du kan bruge skinnet, og vi kan ikke få forbindelse til markedspladsen.

context: %s is the category name (ie. Style or Body)

source_string: This item is unlocked through completing an achievement.
This item is unlocked by completing the %s achievement.
translation: Den genstand låses op ved at opnå %s-gennemførelsen.

source_string: This item was unlocked by completing the %s achievement.
translation: Denne genstand blev låst op ved at opnå %s-gennemførelsen.

source_string: This item is unlocked by completing a challenge from Minecraft Earth.
translation: Låses op ved at klare en udfordring i Minecraft Earth.

source_string: This item was unlocked by completing a challenge from Minecraft Earth.
translation: Låst op ved at klare en udfordring i Minecraft Earth.

source_string: You are switching over to the character creator in this slot. Character creator allows you to build a character in Minecraft item by item. Your classic skin will be saved as a back up in this slot if you want to switch back later.
translation: Du skifter til Karakterudvikler på den aktuelle plads. Karakterudvikler giver dig mulighed for at bygge din karakter i Minecraft del for del. Dit klassiske skin gemmes som backup lige her, hvis du vil skifte tilbage igen senere.

source_string: You are switching over to a classic skin in this slot.  Classic skins are applied to the full character and cannot be customized. Your character creator look will be saved as back up in this slot if you want to switch back later.
translation: Du skifter til et klassisk skin på den aktuelle plads. Klassiske skins anvendes på hele din karakter og kan ikke modificeres. Dit look fra Karakterudvikler gemmes som backup lige her, hvis du vil skifte tilbage igen senere.

source_string: Failed to load character %s. You can reload it from your Profile.
translation: Karakteren %s kunne ikke indlæses. Du kan genindlæse den fra din profil.

source_string: A local or platform skin could not be loaded.
